FlightStats,is,a,cutting,edge,data,services,company,focused,on,commercial,aviation,We,are,the,leading,provider,of,real,time,global,flight,data,to,companies,and,individuals,across,the,travel,ecosystem,The,DelayIndexService,API,returns,a,measure,of,the,level,of,departure,delays,a,specified,airport,is,currently,experiencing,A,low,index,indicates,that,departures,are,running,relatively,smoothly,A,higher,index,is,indicative,of,significant,delays,and,flight,operations,disruptions,The,index,is,updated,every,minutes